Name: Frequency of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ followed by \Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' for cases where activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ leading to a \Request Payment\
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' out of all 'Request Payment'

Name: Frequency of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ in cases with amounts above 100 euros
Metric: Number of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' activities > 100 where ma is the last value of case:Amount

Name: Percentage of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ out of all approval activities
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' out of all cases where 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' does not happen

Name: Number of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ that precede \Payment Handled\
Metric: Number of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' activities for cases where activity 'Payment Handled' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ followed by \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' out of all 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Frequency of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ in cases ending with \Payment Handled\ without \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' for cases where activity 'Payment Handled' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ in cases where \Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE\ occurs more than once
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' out of all 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Number of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ in variants leading to \Payment Handled\ within the shortest performance time
Metric: the minimum of the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Payment Handled'

Name: Percentage of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ in cases exceeding the average case amount
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': 'case:Amount > average'}

Name: Percentage of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ in cases with \Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER\ to identify improvement areas
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' out of all 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Number of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ in the most frequent process variant
Metric: the maximum of the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Percentage of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ in cases that are completed within the top 25% of performance times
Metric: Percentage of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\ in cases that have been rejected at any stage, to identify potential process bottlenecks
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' for cases where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' occurs
